Author: averyfoster11
Text: Fuck, I felt this. Been there, it just made me realize that people are so fucking shallow, and it also fueled my ED bc I didn't want to be mistreated (read: bullied) ever again. I just shut myself in and didn't let anyone close. Tough times, glad it's all behind me now.

Author: -Macaronis-
Text: The next time some old friend that treated you like shit asks you how you've lost so much weight üòç tell them you did it by removing them from your life.
